name: Music_2250.wav
caption: This salsa song contains percussive elements as maracas,cowbell and bongos creating a typical salsa rhythm spread across both sides of the speakers. An e-bass is playing a complex walking bassline. An acoustic piano is playing a melody up and down the scales along with backing vocals singing in harmony as a countermelody to the male lead voice singing in the midrange. This song may be playing in a latin bar.
